{"title":"Linux yum源配置","slug":"Linux-yum源配置","date":"2018-07-17T08:46:43.000Z","updated":"2018-07-18T04:18:14.545Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<h3 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install -y protobuf-vim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"卸载yum安装包\"><a href=\"#卸载yum安装包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"卸载yum安装包\"></a>卸载yum安装包</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum remove -y protobuf-vim.x86_64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"只下载不安装\"><a href=\"#只下载不安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"只下载不安装\"></a>只下载不安装</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install tftp -y --downloadonly --downloaddir=/usr/<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>/src</span><br><span class=\"line\">yum reinstall bash -y --downloadonly --downloaddir=/usr/<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>/src</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>————————————————————————————————————</p>\n<h3 id=\"网易yum源：\"><a href=\"#网易yum源：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网易yum源：\"></a>网易yum源：</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo http://mirrors.163.com/.<span class=\"built_in\">help</span>/CentOS7-Base-163.repo</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">yum clean all</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">yum makecache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"阿里云yum源：\"><a href=\"#阿里云yum源：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"阿里云yum源：\"></a>阿里云yum源：</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/Centos-7.repo</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">yum clean all</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">yum makecache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":[],"tags":[]}